{{italictitle}} {{Infobox book | name = '''Bidayat al Hidayah''' | title_orig = | translator = | image = Bidayat al-Hidayah.PNG | caption = | author = [[Al-Ghazali|Al-Ghazālī]] | illustrator = | cover_artist = | country = [[Persia]] | language = | series = | subject = [[Islamic Law]] and [[Islamic Jurisprudence]] | genre = | publisher = | pub_date = 12th century | english_pub_date = | media_type = | pages = | isbn = | oclc = | dewey = | congress = | preceded_by = | followed_by = }}
'''Bidayat al Hidayah''' ({{lang-ar|بداية الهداية}} {{lang-en|'''The Beginning of Guidance'''|italic=yes}}) was written by [[Abū Ḥāmid Muḥammad ibn Muḥammad al-Ghazālī]] during his last days.<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.pk/books/about/The_Beginning_of_Guidance.html?id=PFgZPQAACAAJ&redir_esc=y |title=The Beginning of Guidance: The Complete English and Arabic Text of Al-Ghazali's Bidayat Al-Hidaya |last=Ghazzālī |date=2005 |publisher=IIC-Classic Series |isbn=9780972272230 |language=en}}</ref> It is a guidebook describing the principles of getting [[Hidayah|guidance]] through [[taqwa]]. The manual is concise and arranged in the form of a daily programme. The book contains three sections, which are on the obedience, refraining from disobedience, and the etiquette of companionship with the [[God in Islam|God]] and His creation.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://seekershub.org/home/courses/ISBGG10A |title=SeekersHub.org - Essentials of Spirituality: Ghazali's Beginning of Guidance Explained (STEP) Part 1 |website=seekershub.org |language=en-US |access-date=2017-11-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911070002/http://seekershub.org/home/courses/ISBGG10A |archivedate=2017-09-11 |df= }}</ref> It serves as a preface to his major texts.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://isnalanterns.com/2015/06/beginning-of-guidance/ |title=Beginning of Guidance |last=Mazhar |first=Mehek |website=Lanterns |language=en-US |access-date=2017-11-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201033726/http://isnalanterns.com/2015/06/beginning-of-guidance/ |archivedate=2017-12-01 |df= }}</ref>
